name: Kunaboto | style
description:
A lora based on the artist kunaboto

I'm surprised no-one on civitai has made one yet so I did so myself

if you like his please,please ,please consider supporting him!!

  • https://www.patreon.com/d3yk7gh4df

Notes

  • To get nipple bikinis ("insert color" swimsuit,nipplebikini) i.e

  • (blue swimsuit,nipplebikini)

  • (pink swimsuit,nipplebikini)

Image info

  • Model used abyssorange2hard

  • bad hands embedding

  • bad artist embedding

  • bad prompt embedding

  • deep negative embedding

Training settings?

The most important part of training is getting a good dataset!

Training settings can be found by installing the additional networks extension in auto1111

Extensions -> available -> load from -> additional networks

Restart webui

place lora into stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora

To view the training settings

Go to additional network tab -> choose model -> training parameters
